bio.p:
Kai Mikkonen(
   kai.mikkonen@helsinki.fi
) is an associate professor of comp-arative literature at the University of Helsinki. He has publishedThe Writer's Metamorphosis(1997),The Plot Machine: The French Novel and the Bachelor Machines in 1880–1914(2001) andKuva ja sana(Image and Word in Interaction, 2005). His current work concerns twentieth-century European travel writing and narrative issues in graphic novels.
